I thought the price for the covered parking garage (about 1/2 block away) was a little steep but we had only one night in New Orleans and asked George if our car could remain in the garage until after room checkout time the next day.	I booked my reservations through a travel web site, they web site stated that parking, $17 a day, would be comped by booking through them.	If you are driving, make sure to ask about the secure parking available (for an extra fee) across the street from the hotel.